des:
"Here is a step by step guide to start controlling your De'Longhi dehumdifier & air purifier with Alexa: 
(1). Download ""De'Longhi Comfort"" app in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2). Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you’re already registered);
(3). Turn on your De'Longhi DDSX dehumdifier & Air purifier and connect it with ""De'Longhi Comfort"" app;
(4) You can rename your heater with De'Longhi Comfort App. In this way, Alexa will recognise the device with that name.
(5). Download Amazon ""Alexa"" app from Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect your smart speaker with ""Alexa"" app;
(6). Search the Alexa Skills directory for ""De'Longhi DDSX dehumifier & air purifier"";
(7). Click Enable skill of ""De'Longhi DDSX dehumidifier & air purifier"", then input your account username, password and region on the linking page;
(8). Finalize the device discovery in Alexa app. You can also say ""Alexa, discover devices.”. Wait till Alexa says ""Discover is completed"";
(9). Now all setup is done and you can start talking to Alexa to control your De'Longhi DDSX dehumidifier & air purifier"
